## PACKAGES

### cli (default)
Path: packages/cli
Spec layers: backend, unit-test
  - .trellis/spec/cli/backend/index.md
  - .trellis/spec/cli/unit-test/index.md

### docs-site [submodule]
Path: docs-site
Spec layers: docs
